Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:09.73,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,"When winds blow," Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:30.05,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, when this poem \Nwas written 800 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.76,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,they must have felt very refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:47.44,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}the only sign of summer is the \Nritual purification in the waters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:44.80,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,They could
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:48.86,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,probably hear the wind blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:55.81,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Silent waves creep closer to the \NSuminoe shore, and when night falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:55.15,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.12,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:00:59.16,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.36,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of dreams, \Nthere's "Silent waves"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:06.58,Chiha-card-TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1317,1)}in my dreams, I creep closer to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:15.51,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:19.36,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:21.55,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,have a good match!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:34.07,Chiha-title2,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1800)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:37.09,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,700)}Verse 13
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:37.09,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,700)}In \Nmy \Ndreams, \NI creep \Ncloser \Nto \Nyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:47.18,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't take the one-syllable card on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.02,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,my opponent's lower right last \Ntime, but I got it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:59.95,Chiha-internal,Su,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent's lower right one-syllable \Ncards are always special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:02.70,Chiha-internal,Su,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking a card from \Nright under their nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.44,Chiha-internal,Su,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.44,Chiha-internal,Su,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase's got the momentum now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.97,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That speed confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.33,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,The neural signal goes straight from \NBellatrix's ears to her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.71,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way \Nto explain her speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.90,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,And another one-syllable "S" card,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:23.47,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,"Swift," was on the opponent's lower left,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.93,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,but she went straight for "Silent."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.31,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That takes guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.84,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That felt very clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:34.91,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I hit the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.65,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I was never able to take \Na card that way before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.86,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, that was a nice attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.61,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:47.41,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you celebrate, \Nyou lose your focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.87,Chiha-poem,,0000,0000,0000,,My own home is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.45,Chiha-poem,,0000,0000,0000,,As the years pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.00,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.32,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.04,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That was a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.05,Chiha-internal,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,As always...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.05,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Good, Megumu isn't \Nletting it get to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.13,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't let the loss \Nof a one-syllable card
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.56,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,from her own side influence her play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:12.39,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I can see why she was the \NWest representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:15.23,Chiha-internal,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi Girls' ace and moodmaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:18.73,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,The match will be decided by \NOusaka Megumu's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.76,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,One more card.  Keep it going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.24,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.66,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I've never played anyone \Nso calm before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:37.16,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}the sight of a midnight moon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.92,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember how to catch momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.69,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,So spring nights are short...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.51,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.07,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Don't back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:44.87,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Fight for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:50.57,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think I got that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:51.10,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:55.80,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you to force \Nher to give you the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:05:01.11,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you end up losing it, the point \Nis to make her feel uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.14,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Throw her off her game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:04.93,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.49,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We touched it at the same time, \Nso it should go to Megumu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.37,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.92,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  You can have it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:12.75,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.04,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She really gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.39,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!  Oh, no!  What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.99,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,So spring ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.11,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.50,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,She was the one who was \Nthrown off her game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.51,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She's not made to contest cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.04,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I need to step up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.52,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I have to step up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.38,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I must step up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.31,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:41.77,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere and audience make \Nit difficult for me to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.78,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,A mountain stream...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.78,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,An empty card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.53,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.11,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.76,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,According to Hanano's notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:02.52,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,the girl with a ponytail had a \Ntowel from an Aoi Ryuji tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.04,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the towel she \Nwas talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.09,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,She actually recognized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.63,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi Ryuji is a singer who's \Nknown for his sappy love songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.17,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Most of them are about broken hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.14,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.52,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,These are the cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.35,Chiha-poem,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I know that my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.01,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.20,Chiha-internal,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.84,Chiha-internal,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that this person is Class C,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:29.86,Chiha-internal,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,but he's tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.87,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find my momentum \Nin my first match today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.69,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I defended that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.12,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take the next one, Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.19,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.45,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san, you're very observant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.04,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:52.81,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}While it brings me no joy, the \Nroad beyond Mount Oe is too long
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.39,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.76,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone got my "While it brings" card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.89,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The momentum is shifting this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.87,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Momentum is when...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.47,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Momentum is when...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.13,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,...you take consecutive cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.02,simple,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Simple-minded
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.98,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,After I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.01,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's so stable...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.67,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.63,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.  Just start with one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.35,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for that one card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.75,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry, Megumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.24,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She's so composed, even on this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.89,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.85,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been with her \Nfor a such a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.01,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and I still don't understand \Nwhat she's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.17,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I got everyone excited \Nabout making her Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:37.48,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,but how does she really feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.27,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Does she want to become Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:44.17,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya isn't able to \Ntake consecutive cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.45,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Her deficit is growing steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.94,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, you just have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.04,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Bring home the win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.55,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say the wrong thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.33,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This is different from last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.52,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,A year has passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:06.77,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,A whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:28.98,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,on a long September night, \Nand then I saw a dawn moon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:36.62,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The sky is the road home \Nfor the holy maidens,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.01,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,An empty card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:35.54,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,She moved immediately, but she \Nwas still able to pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.62,Chiha-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:43.21,Chiha-internal,Rion,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't fall for Ousaka-san's quick reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.97,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.63,GLM,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Good Luck Megumu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.78,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,She's savoring the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.18,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,This is the glory of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:08.16,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,That headband is now an \NOusaka Megumu trademark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:11.15,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be the only \None who wore one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.26,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I made these for Nationals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.57,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:16.50,Chiha-flashback,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.83,Chiha-flashback,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,This is to thank you for \Nthe one you made me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.16,Chiha-flashback,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.97,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful display of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.57,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to be a karuta advisor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.79,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,The reason we worship Megumu-tan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.70,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,is because of the gap in her behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.63,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lenses know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:40.27,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'd look pretty dumb \Nwearing a headband by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.89,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good idea to have \Neveryone else join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.52,swoon,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Swoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:56.53,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,may the wind bring clouds \Nto extend their stay
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.60,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The storm will soon carry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:04.01,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,She went below my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.50,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,She took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:09.02,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,She'd been losing all of the "The" cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.58,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,but that was a clean win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.05,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,Has she figured out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.80,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.17,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, on to the next card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.69,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,One card at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.31,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.38,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,This is a team match,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.99,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,so why am I the only one saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:38.69,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.11,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.59,Chiha-card-TS,,0000,0000,0000,,fades to reveal fishing nets in the shallows
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.89,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,What?  "The hazed early dawn mist"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.23,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's a long multi-syllable card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:56.98,Chiha-internal,B,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.09,Chiha-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, no one would send that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:06.37,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,Multi-syllable cards are supposed \Nto be a weakness for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:07.85,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,Is she sacrificing that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:16.03,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,so I wish for a memory \Nof you to take with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:22.77,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,For you, I would have given up my life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.32,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,A different multi-syllable card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.43,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.17,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The speed when she took \Nthat one-syllable card...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:37.88,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The way she broke my cover...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.63,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel her screaming:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.21,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,"I will become Queen!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.65,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in becoming Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.65,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,but I have to beat her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.53,swoon,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Swoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.88,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,She broke her opponent's cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:20.35,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of players who can
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:21.42,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,take certain cards really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:24.03,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,To win, you have to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.64,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,your weaknesses instead of \Nrelying on your strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.92,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,How much time has she spent practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.04,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,My point is that you're too sloppy \Nabout covering your cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:35.86,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.44,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I \Nhave to repeat myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:44.60,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never become Queen if you \Ncan't conquer your weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.99,Chiha-card-TS,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,now together, I guard it dear
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.99,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.89,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do better if you listen \Ncarefully before moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:53.75,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.53,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:02.76,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:05.71,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.77,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I have to beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:14.80,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,The momentum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:16.55,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,...is shifting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.64,flash,,0000,0000,0000,,Snap Snap
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:18.64,silent,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(126,1)}Taking multiple pictures in silent mode
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.36,flash,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Snap Snap
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.36,silent,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Taking multiple pictures in silent mode
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:25.73,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I hear the beating of cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.57,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:26.99,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I protected mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:27.91,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.41,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Ditto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.62,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.37,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,A-Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.13,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't take three in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.63,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-tan celebrated...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:49.64,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-tan isn't telling her team \Nto focus on the next card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:53.89,Chiha-internal,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.06,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is a high level, \Nback and forth game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:58.15,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pleasantly surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's got good game sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.40,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and a broad field of vision to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.00,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's watching every card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.55,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, \Nshe's always perfectly calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.59,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.10,Chiha-card-TS,,0000,0000,0000,,fades to reveal fishing nets in the shallows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.37,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's returning that multi-syllable card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.10,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.38,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's gotta be a sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:29.85,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The hazed early dawn mist \Nover the Kawagiri River
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.05,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The card she just sent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:29.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She was able to set up a \Nlow cover on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.39,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:37.24,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to keep people \Nfrom breaking my cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:41.60,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I've been practicing with \Neveryone to beat the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.30,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in \Nbecoming Queen though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.15,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to win to \Nmake everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.59,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I have to beat you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.57,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Is she mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.55,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.36,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I still have work to do on \Nmulti-syllable cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:03.67,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:09.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,However, I've realized \Nsomething, Dr. Harada...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.81,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like there are more \Npeople watching our match now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.30,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi Girls'...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.44,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that Ousaka Megumu was \Nthe only threat they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.83,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I was a little excited about my first \Nmatch against an all-girls school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.20,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,May I see you never forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.67,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.66,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,As strong as a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.88,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Ousaka is our engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:47.15,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,but the other girls have also improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:52.23,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,After all, they've been practicing \Nwith Ousaka to help make her Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:56.26,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible to become this \Ngood if you're motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:01.45,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi Girls' is now a team that's \Nimproving themselves for Ousaka's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.77,Chiha-internal,Mina,0000,0000,0000,,Youth...  It brings a tear to my eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.03,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu stopped providing vocal support.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:15.95,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Is her opponent that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.43,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The storm blasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.40,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I was a moment late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.38,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do better...  \NI need to do better...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.20,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,One millimeter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.48,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,One spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.19,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The green border...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.34,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Feel sorrow wash...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:54.07,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember her having \Nsuch a fast motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:58.14,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,Ousaka moved before she did, \Nbut she still took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:00.55,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,That reminded me of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:05.41,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.75,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-chan is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.31,Chiha-flashback,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Stop taking cards with your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.76,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's who I'd be if someone \Nhadn't taught me better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:38.84,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,though autumn is not mine alone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.00,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,A night spent waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.63,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The emotions experienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:53.92,Chiha-internal,Rion,0000,0000,0000,,She finally took three consecutive cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.98,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing flashy about her swing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.93,Chiha-internal,Suo,0000,0000,0000,,but it's accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.40,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,My lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.73,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,My lead is almost gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.32,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.44,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,One card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.84,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,One card at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.26,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I was too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.66,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not used to this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.57,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.39,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of the lonely moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.41,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She swung that hard on an empty card?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.80,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She might as well be a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.80,manly,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Too manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.56,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.24,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:47.45,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that you don't \Ncare about becoming Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.81,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,and you just wanted to \Nhave fun with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:51.73,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:55.60,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu, I'll secure our first win,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.95,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,so you can take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.20,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what \NMegumu is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:03.70,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.20,manly,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.20,manly,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.20,manly,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:10.05,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be playing in the Queen \Nmatch qualifier this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.96,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.84,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,After all, how can you not \Nenjoy becoming stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.97,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu-tan, you're a very gentle girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.94,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,You want to make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.71,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,You want to fulfill their expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:29.86,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,We know that you're working \Nhard for those reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.48,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.64,Chiha-internal,All,0000,0000,0000,,we want to see you succumb \Nto your own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.04,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,As I wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.20,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We touched it at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.34,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But it was on my side, so I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:46.37,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.70,trot,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Trit-Trot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:49.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.36,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,It was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.84,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I won that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:20:01.21,trot,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Trit-Trot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:56.36,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But we touched it at the same \Ntime, and it was on my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.38,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I was faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.89,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.22,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.22,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Megumu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.22,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I was slightly faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.22,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,...is contesting a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.59,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You can take it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.48,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know how to \Ncontest a card, period!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.48,knew,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,1)}I knew it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.53,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.22,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of this team is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.64,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The person who can make \Neveryone happy is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.02,Chiha-internal,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The one who will challenge the Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:29.91,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:31.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.41,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:41.17,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Megumu \Nlike this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.42,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up the card she contested,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.68,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but that makes up for the earlier one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.86,Chiha-internal,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.55,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Just be your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:57.39,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.69,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Time to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.53,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.57,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.07,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:03.75,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,One card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:04.82,Chiha-main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,One card at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:06.32,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.90,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's watching our match.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.33,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,The two teams are even.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.59,Chiha-internal,Rion,0000,0000,0000,,The tension...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:25.31,Chiha-internal,Rion,0000,0000,0000,,The pressure between the two teams is clashing.
